info.author: Tim Jones
info.description:
SDL2 Cython Definition Files
============================

This project includes the definition files for *most* of the SDL2 headers, as well as the headers of
the SDL2 auxilliary libraries SDL2_image, SDL2_mixer and SDL2_ttf.
